38:56.578 --> 39:05.711
Each of you should give what you've decided in your heart to give, not reluctantly or under compulsion for God loves a cheerful giver.

39:07.434 --> 39:25.280
So notice in all three of these public giving calls, the call is to give willingly, not under pressure, not to show off, not to make it about you, but to give willingly and joyfully and celebrate with God's people as they do this together.

39:25.300 --> 39:26.482
Now, if you're a Corinthian,

39:27.106 --> 39:31.453
